        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/wet/scene_rat_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 18324739-f01e-47f4-8c8b-c7f880805491).Image",
        "Description": "Ho-Ho-Ho-Ho, 47!\r\rToday you have to send three incredibly explosive gifts to the people of Chongqing. Your targets were blacklisted by Santa because of what you have to detonate them, and also do it in a beautiful and red Santa suit. Gifts can be placed right under the door, since the Christmas trees are near no residents. I think the task is perfectly clear to you, find and eliminate all the targets.\r\rGood luck, 47!",
